---
// Key features section — homepage
---

<div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-20 lg:px-8 pb-16 sm:pb-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">Funzionalità Chiave</h2>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-700">
      Un'unica piattaforma per gestire il tuo personale: presenze, cantieri, formazione, reportistica e comunicazioni.
    </p>
  </div>
  <dl class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 text-base/7 text-gray-600 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-x-16">
    <div class="relative pl-9">
      <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute top-1 left-1 size-5 text-[#FF6600]">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z" />
        </svg>
        Gestione personale.
      </dt>{" "}
      <dd class="inline">Gestisci i tuoi dipendenti, le loro qualifiche e assegna facilmente compiti e turni in base alle competenze.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="relative pl-9">
      <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute top-1 left-1 size-5 text-[#FF6600]">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m20.893 13.393-1.135-1.135a2.252 2.252 0 0 1-.421-.585l-1.08-2.16a.414.414 0 0 0-.663-.107.827.827 0 0 1-.812.21l-1.273-.363a.89.89 0 0 0-.738 1.595l.587.39c.59.395.674 1.23.172 1.732l-.2.2c-.212.212-.33.498-.33.796v.41c0 .409-.11.809-.32 1.158l-1.315 2.191a2.11 2.11 0 0 1-1.81 1.025 1.055 1.055 0 0 1-1.055-1.055v-1.172c0-.92-.56-1.747-1.414-2.089l-.655-.261a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.383-2.46l.007-.042a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 .29-.787l.09-.15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.37-1.048l1.178.236a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 1.302-.795l.208-.73a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-.578-1.315l-.665-.332-.091.091a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.591.659h-.18c-.249 0-.487.1-.662.274a.931.931 0 0 1-1.458-1.137l1.411-2.353a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 .286-.76m11.928 9.869A9 9 0 0 0 8.965 3.525m11.928 9.868A9 9 0 1 1 8.965 3.525" />
        </svg>
        Multilingua.
      </dt>{" "}
      <dd class="inline">Grazie all'AI i tuoi collaboratori potranno interagire con il sistema con la loro lingua preferita evitando fraintendimenti e perdite di tempo.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="relative pl-9">
      <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute top-1 left-1 size-5 text-[#FF6600]">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
        </svg>
        Monitoraggio presenze.
      </dt>{" "}
      <dd class="inline">Registra in modo automatico le presenze in azienda e sui cantieri, gestisci quotidianamente le anomalie per sede o per reparto.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="relative pl-9">
      <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute top-1 left-1 size-5 text-[#FF6600]">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 0 0-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0 1 12 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 0 1 8.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 0 0-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 0 0-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0 1 12 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0 1 10.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0 1 12 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 0 1 7.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0 1 12 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 0 0 6.75 15.75v-1.5" />
        </svg>
        Corsi di formazione.
      </dt>{" "}
      <dd class="inline">Tieni sotto controllo le scadenze dei corsi obbligatori e le visite mediche dei tuoi collaboratori, grazie al nostro sistema di notifica.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="relative pl-9">
      <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute top-1 left-1 size-5 text-[#FF6600]">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z" />
        </svg>
        Reportistica automatica.
      </dt>{" "}
      <dd class="inline">Abbatti i costi grazie a report dettagliati e personalizzabili su presenze, corsi e avanzamento progetti.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="relative pl-9">
      <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="absolute top-1 left-1 size-5 text-[#FF6600]">
          <path d="M8 16.25a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h2.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-2.5a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75Z" />
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h6a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v12a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H7a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V4Zm4-1.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h2.5a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75V2.5h1A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14.5 4v12a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 5.5 16V4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 7 2.5h1Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        Accesso mobile.
      </dt>{" "}
      <dd class="inline">Lavora ovunque ti trovi. Capi cantieri, Responsabili e Dipendenti possono accedere alle informazioni da qualsiasi dispositivo, in qualsiasi momento.</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
</div>
